{"tid":1992181,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［推到置頂］個個都要入嚟check下自己個選民登記（1 min ONLY）","createTime":"2020-04-28T03:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T16:54:47.000Z","uid":206523,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cfc57bd75e17a5eb7fcbdb4e997163eec9c93d47","tid":1992181,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T03:44:24.000Z","msg":"<strong>你有時間上連登，無時間查下自己有無被遺失？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係佔用你一分鐘時間咋！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你仲記唔記得自己當年有無登記做選民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有登記區議會？咁有無登記立法會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔記得又好，唔清楚又好，都入去睇下啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n網上查閱系統：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/intro.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2Fintro.jsp&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPgu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=78bdc64b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/intro.jsp</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n整撚埋個教學俾你啦，弱智都識啦掛！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vwz3FHh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVwz3FHh.png&h=ba786f4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dLVyiuV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdLVyiuV.png&h=c8c3545f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ND6hLat.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FND6hLat.png&h=29b2ecb0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8a2Wk1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8a2Wk1.png&h=b9d43551&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FxprDzU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFxprDzU.png&h=1cb1d69d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JcDDuHd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJcDDuHd.png&h=7ceb805c&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n（教學完畢）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>屌你老母我唔信你班弱智仔識上連登唔撚識click果兩粒制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n懶就認撚咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果發覺真係無立法會登記選民，<br />\n記得要係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5月2號之前</span></span></strong>交撚咗佢啊！！！<br />\n網上填撚完交就得啦！！！<br />\n網址（同時內有遞交表格的連結）：<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPgu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=ea270b09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a></strong>"},{"pid":"5b78085e3ac05fe2e90e9e8f4df416c9738a3a19","tid":1992181,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T03:44:57.000Z","msg":"自推1次"},{"pid":"2076872fbd526def3a2ce9cc2a6d53d302201fe2","tid":1992181,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T03:45:07.000Z","msg":"自推2次"},{"pid":"21dd2191264c8f9f300ed8b036b6fcc9ce123922","tid":1992181,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T03:45:17.000Z","msg":"自推3次"},{"pid":"4df542fa0ca8b65ac3f273a1743e7272fe1aa43c","tid":1992181,"uid":206523,"like":0,"d